<DATE>03/30/2009</DATE>
<AUTHOR>Nate</AUTHOR>
<TEXT>I only have 117 miles on the car so far, but what I can say is that it is really an experience. I purchase the car for a daily driver in Wisconsin. The ride is not that harsh, the gear box is a MANUAL for all intense purposes and the shifts feel like a good manual transmission would feel. There is a little too much road noise for my personal taste. </TEXT>
<FAVORITE>Engine, BACK SEATS! (good enough for two car seats for the kids!), and price!</FAVORITE>
